Someone seems to have rewritten this page in order to libel this author. Ekman does not write for Steigan.no, Steigan generally copies and pastes articles from other magazines. Whomever has added this to her biography must take a lesson in decency. If she herself did not marry said man, nor had a public rekationship with him, there is no reason why slander from her ex should figure in her biography.
